sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Sui as Sui Predict (OracleSVI)
  participant HL as Hyperliquid HIP-4
  participant LM as Limitless
  participant Eng as Off-Chain Engine
  participant Idx as Postgres Indexer
  participant UI as Dashboard

  Sui-->>Eng: OracleSVIUpdated (WS)
  HL-->>Eng: quote stream (WS)
  LM-->>Eng: quote stream (WS)

  Eng->>Eng: Pricing: fit SVI, BS-invert venues
  Eng->>Eng: Router: pick venue argmax(|Δσ| − fees)
  Eng->>Eng: Risk: gates check

  alt all gates pass
    Eng->>Idx: write cycle (state=Preparing)
    par fire both legs
      Eng->>Sui: predict::mint PTB
      Sui-->>Eng: tx digest
    and
      Eng->>HL: place binary order
      HL-->>Eng: order receipt
    end
    Eng->>Idx: write cycle (state=Live)
    UI-->>Idx: poll, render live tape
    Note over Eng: hold to expiry
    Eng->>Sui: predict::redeem
    Eng->>HL: settle
    Eng->>Idx: write cycle (state=Settled, realized_pnl)
  else any gate fails
    Eng->>Idx: write risk_event, skip cycle
  end
